---
// No props needed
---
<div class="overflow-x-auto my-8">
  <table class="min-w-full bg-white border border-gray-200 shadow-sm rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
    <thead class="bg-brand-navy text-white">
      <tr>
        <th class="py-3 px-4 text-left font-semibold">Service Type</th>
        <th class="py-3 px-4 text-left font-semibold">What it includes</th>
        <th class="py-3 px-4 text-left font-semibold">What it does not include</th>
        <th class="py-3 px-4 text-left font-semibold">Who may provide it</th>
        <th class="py-3 px-4 text-left font-semibold">Legal/Ethical Note</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody class="divide-y divide-gray-200">
      <tr class="hover:bg-gray-50">
        <td class="py-4 px-4 text-brand-navy font-medium align-top">Parent Education & Consultation</td>
        <td class="py-4 px-4 text-gray-700 align-top">General information, developmental milestones, standard behavior strategies, understanding diagnoses broadly.</td>
        <td class="py-4 px-4 text-gray-700 align-top">Individualized medical advice, formal treatment plans, diagnosis.</td>
        <td class="py-4 px-4 text-gray-700 align-top">Child Development Specialists, Consultants, Educators.</td>
        <td class="py-4 px-4 text-gray-500 text-sm align-top">Available internationally without strict jurisdictional limits.</td>
      </tr>
      <tr class="hover:bg-gray-50">
        <td class="py-4 px-4 text-brand-navy font-medium align-top">Developmental Guidance & Behavior Support Planning</td>
        <td class="py-4 px-4 text-gray-700 align-top">Collaborative goal-setting, routine building, identifying triggers, coaching parents on implementing strategies.</td>
        <td class="py-4 px-4 text-gray-700 align-top">Direct therapy with the child, crisis intervention, psychiatric care.</td>
        <td class="py-4 px-4 text-gray-700 align-top">Trained Consultants, Behavior Specialists.</td>
        <td class="py-4 px-4 text-gray-500 text-sm align-top">Focuses on parent coaching rather than direct child treatment.</td>
      </tr>
       <tr class="hover:bg-gray-50">
        <td class="py-4 px-4 text-brand-navy font-medium align-top">School Consultation & IEP Prep</td>
        <td class="py-4 px-4 text-gray-700 align-top">Reviewing school reports, preparing parents for meetings, suggesting classroom accommodations to discuss.</td>
        <td class="py-4 px-4 text-gray-700 align-top">Legal advocacy, enforcing school compliance, diagnosing learning disabilities.</td>
        <td class="py-4 px-4 text-gray-700 align-top">Consultants, Educational Specialists.</td>
        <td class="py-4 px-4 text-gray-500 text-sm align-top">Advisory capacity to empower the parent.</td>
      </tr>
      <tr class="hover:bg-gray-50 bg-red-50">
        <td class="py-4 px-4 text-red-800 font-medium align-top">Psychological Therapy & Assessment</td>
        <td class="py-4 px-4 text-gray-700 align-top">Diagnosing conditions (ASD/ADHD), administering standardized psychological tests, treating mental health disorders.</td>
        <td class="py-4 px-4 text-gray-700 align-top">N/A (This is the regulated service).</td>
        <td class="py-4 px-4 text-gray-700 align-top">Licensed/Registered Psychologists.</td>
        <td class="py-4 px-4 text-red-700 text-sm font-medium align-top">Strictly limited to the jurisdiction where the provider holds an active license/registration.</td>
      </tr>
      <tr class="hover:bg-gray-50 bg-red-50">
        <td class="py-4 px-4 text-red-800 font-medium align-top">Emergency Care</td>
        <td class="py-4 px-4 text-gray-700 align-top">Immediate intervention for risk of harm, severe psychiatric crisis.</td>
        <td class="py-4 px-4 text-gray-700 align-top">Ongoing therapy.</td>
        <td class="py-4 px-4 text-gray-700 align-top">Local emergency services, hospitals.</td>
        <td class="py-4 px-4 text-red-700 text-sm font-medium align-top">Must be handled by local, immediate responders. Online platforms cannot provide this.</td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</div>
